Name: Endodontics Using Rotary Instruments: A Step-by-Step Predictable Approach
Subject: Endodontics
Short Description: This course will discuss step-by-step procedures that will give you a more predictable outcome for the endodontic portion of your practice. We will discuss the five tests to determine pulpal and periradicular diagnosis. We will also discuss the best anesthetic techniques for treating the endodontic patient that can’t quite get “numb” enough. We will also talk about pain medication and antibiotics for the post-operative patient.Read More

Name: THE DANGERS OF VAPING THC: WHAT HEALTH PROFESSIONALS NEED TO KNOW
Subject: Oral Pathology/Medicine
Short Description: Review the history of vaping. Outline the difference between vaping and smoking. Outline the difference between THC and nicotine vaping. Describe the increase in “youth vaping” of THC, CBD, and synthetic cannabinoids in America. Explain the real evidence (or lack thereof) for EVALI and vaping disease. List the difference between THC Oil, Marijuana Oil, Cannabis Oil, Hash Oil, CBD Oil and Hemp Oil. Review the critical Adverse Reactions that occur with vaping THC.Read More
